{"title":"hsl to rgb converter","description":"A program that allows you to quickly convert hsl to rgb online.","content":"## About the hsl to rgb converter\r\nThis converter allows you to convert a color represented by the **HSL** color model to **RGB**\r\nAs a result of the conversion, you will get three numbers, the values ​​of which reflect the degree of presence of red, green and blue colors according to the **RGB** model.\r\nThis program, respectively, can also perform reverse conversion, that is, [convert rgb to hsl] (color / rgb_to_hsl).\r\n\r\n## How to convert hsl to rgb\r\nTo convert hsl to rgb, enter the value of the hue, saturation level and brightness in the appropriate fields.\r\nThe **RGB** value will be immediately calculated and displayed in three fields for each primary color: red, green and blue."}